    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Strict synchronous request/reply. The Requester sends a message and must call recv before sending again. Useful for control plane messages (e.g. tuning commands, metadata queries) and signal-frame RPC. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
